Do not resist! Get out of the car!

209
00:15:59.166 --> 00:16:02.250
This is the police. Do not resist!

210
00:16:02.333 --> 00:16:04.166
<i>Do not resist!</i>

211
00:16:09.875 --> 00:16:12.458
I will spare your life.

212
00:16:14.958 --> 00:16:17.625
