233
00:18:06.833 --> 00:18:08.083
Fuck you!

234
00:18:08.166 --> 00:18:09.625
Let's play together.

235
00:18:09.708 --> 00:18:11.750
- No. fuck off!
- Let's go!

236
00:18:11.833 --> 00:18:13.166
Fuck you!

237
00:18:14.916 --> 00:18:16.125
Motherfucker!

238
00:18:22.375 --> 00:18:23.250
